{"lessonId":"480","lessonName":"[CONVERSATIONS] - 82. An Interesting Movie","audioSrc":"","challenges":[{"id":18669,"position":1,"content":"I thought that movie was terrific, didn't you?","jsonContent":["I","thought","that","movie","was","terrific,",["didn't","did not"],"you?"],"solution":[["I"],["thought"],["that"],["movie"],["was"],["terrific,"],["didn't","did not"],["you?"]],"audioSrc":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/82-an-interesting-movie-2022-03-07-21-31-24/1.mp3"},{"id":18670,"position":2,"content":"I don't know. It didn't seem to have any meaning.","jsonContent":["I",["don't","do not"],"know.","It",["didn't","did not"],"seem","to","have","any","meaning."],"solution":[["I"],["don't","do not"],["know."],["It"],["didn't","did not"],["seem"],["to"],["have"],["any"],["meaning."]],"audioSrc":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/82-an-interesting-movie-2022-03-07-21-31-24/2.mp3"},{"id":18671,"position":3,"content":"Come on. It seems that you expect intellectual stimulation from every movie.","jsonContent":["Come","on.","It","seems","that","you","expect","intellectual","stimulation","from","every","movie."],"solution":[["Come"],["on."],["It"],["seems"],["that"],["you"],["expect"],["intellectual"],["stimulation"],["from"],["every"],["movie."]],"audioSrc":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/82-an-interesting-movie-2022-03-07-21-31-24/3.mp3"},{"id":18672,"position":4,"content":"I just think that a good movie should have a central theme at least.","jsonContent":["I","just","think","that","a","good","movie","should","have","a","central","theme","at","least."],"solution":[["I"],["just"],["think"],["that"],["a"],["good"],["movie"],["should"],["have"],["a"],["central"],["theme"],["at"],["least."]],"audioSrc":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/82-an-interesting-movie-2022-03-07-21-31-24/4.mp3"},{"id":18673,"position":5,"content":"Yes. But it doesn't hurt you to watch a funny movie once in a while.","jsonContent":["Yes.","But","it",["doesn't","does not"],"hurt","you","to","watch","a","funny","movie","once","in","a","while."],"solution":[["Yes."],["But"],["it"],["doesn't","does not"],["hurt"],["you"],["to"],["watch"],["a"],["funny"],["movie"],["once"],["in"],["a"],["while."]],"audioSrc":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/82-an-interesting-movie-2022-03-07-21-31-24/5.mp3"},{"id":18674,"position":6,"content":"Relax and enjoy it!","jsonContent":["Relax","and","enjoy","it!"],"solution":[["Relax"],["and"],["enjoy"],["it!"]],"audioSrc":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/82-an-interesting-movie-2022-03-07-21-31-24/6.mp3"},{"id":18675,"position":7,"content":"You're right. I'm too serious sometimes.","jsonContent":[["You're","you are"],"right.",["I'm","I am"],"too","serious","sometimes."],"solution":[["You're","you are"],["right."],["I'm","I am"],["too"],["serious"],["sometimes."]],"audioSrc":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/82-an-interesting-movie-2022-03-07-21-31-24/7.mp3"}]}